Quickstrike:




With his body low, Quickstrike looked to Dark Mouse. He still had a 
nervous look on his scorpion face, but he had to act like everything 
was fine. 

So, they weren't going back to Megatron, that was a plus for them. 
Both of them. 

"We keep goin' then, huh?" he said to Dark Mouse. They were halfway 
to their destination.
